data.name: Son' Restaurant
data.description: Invite the guest to discover the world and culinary imagination of this young chef , he wanted a place to fresh atmosphere that allows our guest to forget the bustle of the city. His wish is to take you ' to amaze and delight you with a clean kitchen, simple and unique. Exclusively from fresh produce , the chef likes to work and imagine the perfect combination of a vegetable , meat or fish, spice and sauce juices outcome and reducing firings. Street Side Restaurant is a serene and peaceful place dedicated to gluttony . Between the kitchen and the Landes pine tables , everything has been studied to ensure you a great time. The wish of the Chief carry with him into the vortex of Youth and flavors as long as possible .

data.name: Suzzi
data.description: Suzzi is a swedish cafe/brunch located in the heart of Bordeaux city. Arvid & Margaux offer delicious swedish dishes for lunch, brunch (available every day) as well as their famous cinammon rolls. On the menu: open-faced sandwiches, swedish pancakes, waffles, pastries, homemade drinks, organic coffee & tea. Homemade food with love in a scandinavian atmosphere...

data.name: Le Chicoula
data.description: « De tous les arts, l’art culinaire est celui qui nourrit le mieux…» Pierre Dac Chicoula : du provençal siroter, déguster. Notre projet s’inscrit dans notre philosophie de vie épicurienne et de notre goût pour les échanges interculturels. Après plusieurs voyages, plusieurs rencontres, nous souhaitons transmettre, partager etnous vous invitons au voyage culinaire. Notre chef réalise une ardoise gourmande qui évolue au grès des saisons et avec le travail de nos producteurs locaux, servi et accompagné d’une sélection de vins choisis. Bienvenue…

data.name: Dans le Noir ? Bordeaux
data.description: More than a restaurant, Dans le Noir ? is an international brand with a unique concept where patrons dine in complete darkness, guided and served by amazing and unexpected staff. An original experience that has intrigued and awakened the minds of millions of people for more than 15 years. Your senses are awakened and invite you to an unforgettable culinary journey! Discover now this unique sensory, social and human experience in all our venues around the world: London, Paris, Madrid, Barcelona, Saint Petersburg, Auckland, Melbourne, Marrakech, Nantes, Bordeaux.

L'assurance d'un accueil attentionné & singulier par Carl Vaillant (le Fils). En cuisine, Stéphane Vaillant (le Père), et le Chef Richard vous préparent de belles assiettes gourmandes & saines. Viandes, Poissons et autres mets spécifiques aux Végétariens comme Végétaliens. Bref, une offre pour tous les régimes alimentaires et toutes les gourmandises !

photo.caption: Fraisoffee sur commande chez Mi Cielo

data.description: Welcome to Mi Cielo Pâtisserie, a French fine pastry shop with an exotic flair located in the vibrant city of Bordeaux, France. Our philosophy; indulge our clients with a culinary experience filled with flavorful and seasonal fresh ingredients. Everything we do is from scratch and we’re proud of it! In addition, we don’t use any artificial colorants or flavors to our delicious sweet treats. You can be sure that you will have the best quality with every product we offer at our boutique. We also try to support our community by buying local raw materials. Our big cakes are made only on demand to guarantee freshness!

data.name: Le Bistrot des Anges
data.description: "A traditional Bordeaux eatery just moments from the banks of the Garonne River, the Bistrot des Anges offers a welcoming atmosphere, friendly service and pleasant surroundings - the ideal foil to a mouthwatering menu of classic French dishes. Intimate and cosy, the interior has the feel of a family dining room with tables close together and a buzz of conversation on the air. But when the sun comes out there's competition for seats on the sun trap terrace, a lovely escape from the city streets where the food seems to taste even sweeter. The extensive menu offers something for everyone with a strong lean towards flavours from the South West of France. "

THE AMBIANCE - Very friendly, the atmosphere at Gourmands will immediately bring a smile to your face, you should definitely come and try it for yourself!
